    Layout

    
 struct b3CollisionShapeData {
     int m_objectUniqueId;
     int m_linkIndex;
     int m_collisionGeometryType;
     double m_dimensions[3];
     double m_localCollisionFrame[7];
     char m_meshAssetFileName[VISUAL_SHAPE_MAX_PATH_LEN];
 }
